title: The Parthenon Greek Grill
typeOfFood: Lacto, Mediterranean, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Greek, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Greek food restaurant. Menu includes some vegetarian suitable dishes like the house-made hummus, vegetable sides, pasta, dolmas, moussaka, pastitsio, a falafel sandwich, and a grilled veggie wrap. Could request vegan and kitchen will accommodate if possible. Salad portions are generous, but vegans must specify no feta cheese.
